How To Improve Communication Skills:

Always think what they want - Art of Communication
Always be Warm and Friendly - 
Always Talk Less and Give More Value
Always have ice breakers - Cold reading 
Always Spark Curiosity
Always Communicate with yourself first - RRR Formula - Read, Record & Repeat.
Always Speak with clarity - For Effective communication
       Always be Authentic while speaking
       Give a breathing space while speaking  - chill & slow.




